        <body>
            <entry xml:id="entry_amæntyn" xml:lang="os">
                <form xml:id="form_d1704e66" xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>amæntyn</orth><form xml:id="form_d1704e68" type="participle"><orth>amæst</orth></form></form>
                <form xml:id="form_d1704e71" xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>amætun</orth><form xml:id="form_d1704e73" type="participle"><orth>amast</orth></form></form>
                <sense xml:id="sense_d1704e76"><sense xml:id="sense_d1704e77"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>месить тесто</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>beat dough</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense xml:id="sense_d1704e86"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>мазать</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>smear</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense><sense xml:id="sense_d1704e95"><abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>марать</q>
                        </abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>stain</q>
                        </abv:tr></sense></sense>
                <abv:exampleGrp>
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d1704e107">
                        <quote>dæxī kæm samæstaj?</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>где ты испачкался?</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>where did you get dirty?</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                    </abv:example>
                    <abv:example xml:id="example_d1704e122">
                        <quote>Satana ærtæ mydamæsty rakodta</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>Шатана приготовила три заквашенные с медом лепешки</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>Shatana made three flatbreads fermented with honey</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_ЮОПам."/><biblScope>I
                            133</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Восходит к *ā-mamθ-. Старое сращение преверба %iа%i- с основой
                    %imanθ%i ‘мешать’, ‘размешивать’, ‘болтать’; ср. <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d1704e144" xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>ā-mant- : ā-masta-</w>
                        <gloss><q>повреждать (толкая, ударяя)</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d1704e152" xml:lang="kho"><lang/>
                        <w>maṃth(-mant)</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d1704e157" xml:lang="prc"><lang/>
                        <w>menth-</w>
                        <gloss><q>марать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d1704e165" xml:lang="ps"><lang/>
                        <w>mand-(ksemandəl)</w>
                        <gloss><q>месить</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d1704e173" xml:lang="wbl"><lang/>
                        <w>mānd-</w>
                        <gloss><q>натирать</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d1704e182" xml:lang="isk"><lang/>
                        <w>mənd</w>
                        <gloss><q>мазать</q></gloss></mentioned>. Сращение той же основы с превербом
                    %iyz%i- имеем в глаголе <ref type="xr" target="#entry_yzmæntyn"/> | %iæzmæntun%i
                    ‘мешать’, ‘мутить’. Без превербов глагола *%imæntyn%i осетинский не знает.
                    Дальнейшее см. под <ref type="xr" target="#entry_yzmæntyn"/>.</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">It traces back to *%iā-mamθ%i-. An old fusion of the preverb
                    %iа%i- with the stem %imanθ%i ‘mix’, ‘stir’, ‘shake’; cf. <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d1704e198" xml:lang="ae"><lang/>
                        <w>ā-mant- : ā-masta-</w>
                        <gloss><q>damage (by pushing, hitting)</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d1704e206" xml:lang="kho"><lang/>
                        <w>maṃth(-mant)</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d1704e211" xml:lang="prc"><lang/>
                        <w>menth-</w>
                        <gloss><q>stain</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d1704e219" xml:lang="ps"><lang/>
                        <w>mand-(ksemandəl)</w>
                        <gloss><q>mash</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d1704e227" xml:lang="wbl"><lang/>
                        <w>mānd-</w>
                        <gloss><q>polish</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:id="mentioned_d1704e236" xml:lang="isk"><lang/>
                        <w>mənd</w>
                        <gloss><q>smear</q></gloss></mentioned>. The fusion of the same stem with
                    the preverb %iyz%i- is found in the verb <ref type="xr" target="#entry_yzmæntyn"/> | %iæzmæntun%i ‘mix’, ‘puddle’. There is no verb *%imæntyn%i without preverbs
                    in Ossetic. See further information under the word <ref type="xr" target="#entry_yzmæntyn"/>.</etym>
            </entry>
